origin: If the specified file does not exist, it will be created using default properties. Otherwise, it is opened in read and write mode with default access properties. Any operations except dscreate() functions on object will be thread safe. Multiple datasets can be created inside a single hdf5 file, and can be accessed from the same hdf5 object from multiple instances as long read or write operations are done over non-overlapping regions of dataset. Single hdf5 file also can be opened by multiple instances, reads and writes can be instantiated at the same time as long as non-overlapping regions are involved. Object is released using close().
local: 如果指定的文件不存在，则将使用默认属性创建该文件。否则，它将以读写模式以默认访问属性打开。对象上除dscreate（）函数以外的任何操作都是线程安全的。可以在一个hdf5文件中创建多个数据集，并且可以从多个实例的同一hdf5对象访问多个数据集，只要在数据集的非重叠区域上执行长时间的读写操作即可。单个hdf5文件也可以由多个实例打开，只要涉及非重叠区域，就可以同时实例化读写。使用close（）释放对象。
